                            <comment id="13890411" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 4 Feb 2014 05:44:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;On the first hunk, should &lt;tt&gt;indexManager.getIndexForColumn(expression.column_name)&lt;/tt&gt; even be including non-CF indexes?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13890852" author="sbtourist" created="Tue, 4 Feb 2014 17:04:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d say so, it&apos;s still an index and it&apos;s useful to retrieve it from column names, whether it is backed by a CF or not.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
